l="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259284/oura-ring-samsung-galaxy-ring-ultra human-ring-air-ringconn-circular-ring-evie-ring-review-wearables</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-01T12:50:01-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-01T12:50:01-04:00</updated><title>东部和墨西哥湾沿岸的港口工人举行罢工</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示美国码头工人罢工的照片&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/37pygfWZdJrzPW5aIeJmd7ohtac=/0x3:8192x5464/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/73624635/2175263694.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Getty&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;FZ90mN&quot;>;美国东部和墨西哥湾沿岸的数十个港口已关闭随着数千名码头工人罢工，抗议可能取代工作的工资和技术，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cnbc.com/2024/10/01/east-coast-ports-strike-ila-union-work -stop-billions-in-trade.html&quot;>;据 CNBC&lt;/a>; 报道。这次罢工于 10 月 1 日午夜刚过，可能会提高价格，并使货物更难获得，具体取决于罢工持续的时间。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Fq5xdy&quot;>;国际码头工人协会 (ILA)，代表约 85,000 名码头工人的工会在与支持港口雇主的组织美国海事联盟 (USMX) 的合同于周二凌晨到期后发起了罢工。罢工涵盖从缅因州到德克萨斯州的港口。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ylqZBA&quot;>;与 USMX 的新合同谈判仍在进行中 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ajot.com/insights /full/ai-usmx-says-it-ila-have-traded-counter-offers-linked-to-wages&quot;>;提议加薪 50%&lt;/a>;。沿着...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259395/port-workers-ila-east-gulf-coast-strike-automation&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259395/port-workers-ila-east-gulf-coast-strike-automation" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259395/port-workers-ila-east-gulf-coast-strike-automation</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-01T12:28:22-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-01T12:28:22-04:00</updated><title> Epic 正在努力促成使用虚幻引擎和 Epic Games Store 的交易</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Epic Games 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/YrjzuQOi1ivZKMipy8o8hSwFbdU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/ image/73624589/acastro_STK108__01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Alex Castro / The Verge 的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;OiyDse&quot;>;Epic 为使用虚幻构建游戏的开发者提供更好的条款引擎并在 Epic Games Store 上列出它们。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;YVaUQa&quot;>;作为新的“Launch Everywhere with Epic”计划的一部分，Epic 正在将使用虚幻引擎构建的游戏的版税从 5% 降低到 3.5%——但是，这些游戏必须在发布当天在 Epic Games Store 上提供。该计划将于 2025 年 1 月 1 日启动，适用于当年开始在 Epic Games Store 上发布的符合条件的游戏。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;xDOLiN&quot;>;通过这一举措，Epic 似乎还在尝试&lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2023/8/23/23843018/epic-games-store-first-run-developers-revenue&quot;>;鼓励开发者在其商店上架游戏的另一种方式&lt;/a>;，包括其新推出的商店&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/16/24221361/fortnite-iphone-epic-games-app-store&quot;>;Android 和 iOS 版&lt;/a>;。 Epic 表示，开发者所在的每个平台和商店都将享受版税减免。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24258723 /epic-games-store-unreal-engine-launch-everywhere-royalty&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24258723/epic-games-store-unreal-engine-launch-everywhere-royalty" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24258723/epic-games-store-unreal-engine-launch-everywhere-royalty</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry></feed>